<p source="GUODIAN.ZIYI 5.1. SLIPS 1-2 "><pb xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-1a" ed="tls" n="001-1a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-1a.1">夫子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-1a.2">好美如好緇衣，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-1a.3">惡惡如惡巷伯，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-1a.4">則民咸服(力LL)</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-1a.5">而刑不蠢 (頓LL)。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-1a.6">《詩》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-1a.7">「儀型文王，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-1a.8">萬邦作孚。」</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN.ZIYI 5.2. SLIPS 2-3"><pb xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-2a" ed="tls" n="001-2a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-2a.1">子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-2a.2">有國者章好章惡，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-2a.3">以示民厚，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-2a.4">則民情不忒。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-2a.5">《詩》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-2a.6">「靖共爾位，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-2a.7">好是正直。」</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN.ZIYI 5.3. SLIPS 3-5 "><pb xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-3a" ed="tls" n="001-3a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-3a.1">子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-3a.2">為上可望而知也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-3a.3">為下可類 [述 SMR1:87]而等也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-3a.4">則君不疑其臣，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-3a.5">臣不惑於君。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-3a.6">《詩》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-3a.7">「淑人君子，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-3a.8">其儀不忒。」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-3a.9">《尹誥》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-3a.10">「惟伊尹及湯，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-3a.11">咸有一德。」</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN.ZIYI 5.4. SLIPS 5-7 "><pb xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-4a" ed="tls" n="001-4a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-4a.1">子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-4a.2">上人疑</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-4a.3">則百姓惑，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-4a.4">下難知</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-4a.5">則君長勞。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-4a.6">故君民者章好</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-4a.7">以示民欲，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-4a.8">謹惡</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-4a.9">以御[渫QXG]民淫，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-4a.10">則民不惑。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-4a.11">臣事君，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-4a.12">言其所不能，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-4a.13">不辭其所能，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-4a.14">則君不勞。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN.ZIYI 5.5. SLIPS 7-8 "><pb xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-5a" ed="tls" n="001-5a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-5a.1">《大雅》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-5a.2">「上帝板板，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-5a.3">下民卒癉[疸LL]。」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-5a.4">《小雅》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-5a.5">「非其止之共,  [=非其止共]</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-5a.6">唯王恭 [邛LL]。[唯王之邛RT; ES 99 n.50]」</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN.ZIYI 5.6. SLIPS 8- 9"><pb xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-6a" ed="tls" n="001-6a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-6a.1">子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-6a.2">民以君為心，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-6a.3">君以民為體，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-6a.4">心好則體安之，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-6a.5">君好則民欲之。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-6a.6">故心以體廢，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-6a.7">君以民亡。</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN.ZIYI 5.7. SLIPS 9-10"><pb xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-7a" ed="tls" n="001-7a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-7a.1">《詩》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-7a.2">「誰秉國成?</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-7a.3">不自為貞[正GDE]，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-7a.4">卒勞百姓。」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-7a.5">《君牙》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-7a.6">「日暑雨，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-7a.7">小 民惟日怨；</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-7a.8">晉冬耆滄，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-7a.9">小民亦惟日怨。」</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN.ZIYI 5.8. SLIPS 10-12"><pb xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-8a" ed="tls" n="001-8a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-8a.1">子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-8a.2">上好仁</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-8a.3">則下之為仁也</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-8a.4">爭先。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-8a.5">故長民者彰 [章GDE]志</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-8a.6">以昭百姓，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-8a.7">則民致行己</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-8a.8">以悅上。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-8a.9">《詩》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-8a.10">「有覺德行，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-8a.11">四方順之。」</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN.ZIYI 5.9. SLIPS 12-14"><pb xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-9a" ed="tls" n="001-9a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-9a.1">子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-9a.2">禹立三年，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-9a.3">百姓以仁道，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-9a.4">豈必 盡仁。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-9a.5">《詩》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-9a.6">「成王之孚，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-9a.7">下土之式。」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-9a.8">《呂型》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-9a.9">「一人有慶，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-9a.10">萬民賴 之。」</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN.ZIYI 5.10. SLIPS 14-16"><pb xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-10a" ed="tls" n="001-10a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-10a.1">子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-10a.2">下之事上也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-10a.3">不從其所以命，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-10a.4">而從其所行。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-10a.5">上好此物也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-10a.6">下必有甚焉者矣。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-10a.7">故上之好惡，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-10a.8">不可不慎也。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-10a.9">民之表也。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-10a.10">《詩》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-10a.11">「赫赫師尹，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-10a.12">民具爾瞻。」</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN.ZIYI 5.11. SLIPS 16-17"><pb xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-11a" ed="tls" n="001-11a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-11a.1">子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-11a.2">長民者衣服不改，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-11a.3">從容有常，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-11a.4">則民德 一。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-11a.5">《詩》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-11a.6">「其容不改，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-11a.7">出言有章[順LL]，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-11a.8">黎民所望[信LL]。」</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN.ZIYI 5.12. SLIPS 17-19"><pb xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-12a" ed="tls" n="001-12a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-12a.1">子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-12a.2">大人不親其所賢，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-12a.3">而 信其所賤，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-12a.4">教此以失，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-12a.5">民此以變[煩LL]。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-12a.6">《詩》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-12a.7">「彼求我則，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-12a.8">如不我得，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-12a.9">執我 仇仇，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-12a.10">亦不我力。」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-12a.11">《君陳》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-12a.12">「未見聖，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-12a.13">如其弗克見，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-12a.14">我既見，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-12a.15">我弗迪聖。」</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN.ZIYI 5.13. SLIPS 19-23"><pb xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-13a" ed="tls" n="001-13a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-13a.1">子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-13a.2">大臣之不親也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-13a.3">則忠敬不足，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-13a.4">而富貴已過也。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-13a.5">邦家之不寧 也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-13a.6">則大臣不治，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-13a.7">而褻臣託也。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-13a.8">此以大臣不可不敬，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-13a.9">民之蕝也。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-13a.10">故君不與小謀大，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-13a.11">則大臣不怨。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-13a.12">《葉[祭SHR1:112 n.5] 公之顧命》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-13a.13">「毋以小謀敗大圖，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-13a.14">毋以嬖御塞莊后，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-13a.15">毋以嬖士塞大夫，卿士」</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN.ZIYI 5.14. SLIPS 23-27"><pb xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-14a" ed="tls" n="001-14a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-14a.1">子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-14a.2">長民者</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-14a.3">教之 以德，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-14a.4">齊之以禮，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-14a.5">則民有勸心，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-14a.6">教之以政，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-14a.7">齊之以刑，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-14a.8">則民有免心。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-14a.9">故孳以愛之，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-14a.10">則民有親，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-14a.11">信以結之，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-14a.12">則民不倍，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-14a.13">恭以莅[蒞LL]之，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-14a.14">則民有遜心。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-14a.15">《詩》云：</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN.ZIYI 5.15. SLIPS 27-29"><pb xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-15a" ed="tls" n="001-15a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-15a.1">子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-15a.2">政之不行，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-15a.3">教之不成也，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-15a.4">則刑罰不 足恥，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-15a.5">而爵不足勸也。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-15a.6">故上不可以褻刑</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-15a.7">而輕爵。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-15a.8">《康誥》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-15a.9">「敬 明乃罰。」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-15a.10">《呂刑》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-15a.11">「播刑之迪。」</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN.ZIYI 5.16. SLIPS 29-30"><pb xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-16a" ed="tls" n="001-16a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-16a.1">子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-16a.2">王言如絲，其出如綸[(糸+昏)= 綸 SHR1: 126 n.1]；</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-16a.3">王言如索, 其出如(糸+聿)[紼LL]。故大人不倡流。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-16a.4">《詩》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-16a.5">「慎爾出話，敬爾威儀。」</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN.ZIYI 5.17. SLIPS 30-32"><pb xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-17a" ed="tls" n="001-17a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-17a.1">子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-17a.2">可言不可行，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-17a.3">君子弗言；</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-17a.4">可行不可言，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-17a.5">君子弗行。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-17a.6">則民言不危行，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-17a.7">〔行 ES: 111 n.76〕不危 言。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-17a.8">《詩》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-17a.9">「淑慎爾止，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-17a.10">不諐(衍LL)于儀。」</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN.ZIYI 5.18. SLIPS 32-34"><pb xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-18a" ed="tls" n="001-18a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-18a.1">子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-18a.2">君子道人以言，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-18a.3">而恒以行。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-18a.4">故言則慮其所終，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-18a.5">行則稽其所敝，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-18a.6">則民慎於言，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-18a.7">而謹於行。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-18a.8">《詩》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-18a.9">「穆穆 文王，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-18a.10">於緝熙敬止。」</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN.ZIYI 5.19. SLIPS 34-37"><pb xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-19a" ed="tls" n="001-19a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-19a.1">子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-19a.2">言從行之，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-19a.3">則行不可匿。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-19a.4">故君子顧言</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-19a.5">而行，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-19a.6">以成其信，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-19a.7">則民不能大其美</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-19a.8">而小其惡。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-19a.9">《大雅》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-19a.10">「白珪之玷，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-19a.11">尚可磨也。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-19a.12">此言之玷，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-19a.13">不可為也。」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-19a.14">《小雅》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-19a.15">「允也君子，</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN.ZIYI 5.20. SLIPS 37-40"><pb xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-20a" ed="tls" n="001-20a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-20a.1">子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-20a.2">君子言有物，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-20a.3">行有格，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-20a.4">此以生不可奪志，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-20a.5">死不可奪名。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-20a.6">故君子多聞，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-20a.7">齊而守之；</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-20a.8">多志，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-20a.9">齊而親之；</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-20a.10">精知，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-20a.11">略而行之。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-20a.12">《詩》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-20a.13">「淑人君子，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-20a.14">其儀一也。」</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-20a.15">《君陳》云：</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN.ZIYI 5.21. SLIPS 40-41"><pb xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-21a" ed="tls" n="001-21a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-21a.1">子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-21a.2">苟有車，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-21a.3">必見其蓋。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-21a.4">苟有衣，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-21a.5">必見其黻。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-21a.6">人苟有言，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-21a.7">必聞其聲；</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-21a.8">苟有行，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-21a.9">必見其成。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-21a.10">《詩》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-21a.11">「服之亡懌[斁RT]。」</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN.ZIYI 5.22. SLIPS 41-42"><pb xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-22a" ed="tls" n="001-22a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-22a.1">子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-22a.2">私惠不懷德，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-22a.3">君子不自留焉。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-22a.4">《詩》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-22a.5">「人之好我，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-22a.6">示我周行。」</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN.ZIYI 5.23. SLIPS 42-43"><pb xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-23a" ed="tls" n="001-23a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-23a.1">子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-23a.2">唯君子能好其匹，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-23a.3">小人豈能好其匹。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-23a.4">故君子之友也 有鄉[向LL]，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-23a.5">其惡有方。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-23a.6">此以邇者不惑，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-23a.7">而遠者不疑。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-23a.8">《詩》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-23a.9">「君子好逑。」</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN.ZIYI 5.24. SLIPS 43-45"><pb xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-24a" ed="tls" n="001-24a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-24a.1">子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-24a.2">輕 絕貧賤，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-24a.3">而重絕富貴，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-24a.4">則好仁不堅，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-24a.5">而惡不著也。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-24a.6">人雖曰不利，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-24a.7">吾弗信之矣。</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-24a.8">《詩》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-24a.9">「朋友攸攝，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-24a.10">攝以威儀。」</seg></p>

<p source="GUODIAN.ZIYI 5.25. SLIPS 45-47"><pb xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-25a" ed="tls" n="001-25a"/>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-25a.1">子曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-25a.2">宋人有言曰：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-25a.3">“人而亡恒，</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-25a.4">不可為卜筮也.”</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-25a.5">其古之遺言與？</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-25a.6">龜筮猶弗知</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-25a.7">而況於人乎？</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-25a.8">《詩》云：</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-25a.9">「我龜既厭,</seg>
<seg xml:id="KR2p0018_tls_001-25a.10">不我告猷。」</seg></p>

